transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Hey, thanks for calling Viagra, how can I help you?

Speaker 2: Hey, I wanted to check on the order to replace, the status of it.

Speaker 1: See how long it's going to take to ship.

Speaker 2: What was your first and last name?

Speaker 1: Eric, last name's Cap, K-A-P-P.

Speaker 2: All right, Mr. Cap, I see the order is still going through the process.

Speaker 1: You should see this approved and shipped out by tomorrow.

Speaker 2: Okay, and then how long does it usually take to ship?

Speaker 1: Three to five business days with USPS, that's just the regular shipping time frame.

Speaker 2: So you'll probably see that order by this upcoming Tuesday.

Speaker 1: Okay, cool.

Speaker 2: Thank you, sir.

Speaker 1: Well, actually, hey, you know what, how many of those pills are they sending?

Speaker 2: We've got 20 pills coming out, it looks like, 100 milligrams.

Speaker 1: All right, cool. Thank you, sir.

Speaker 2: No problem, thank you.
